## Design System Quick Reference

**Fonts:** `Inter` (all text) ┬╖ `JetBrains Mono` (code)
**Colors:**
- Primary: `#185FA5` ┬╖ Dark: `#0C447C` ┬╖ Light bg: `#E6F1FB`
- Success: `#1D9E75` ┬╖ Error: `#D93025` ┬╖ Warning: `#F59E0B`
- Text: `#2C2C2A` ┬╖ Secondary text: `#6B7280` ┬╖ Disabled: `#9CA3AF`
- Border: `#D1DCE8` ┬╖ Surface: `#FFFFFF` ┬╖ Page bg: `#F4F8FC`

**Radius:** Inputs/buttons `8px` ┬╖ Cards `12px` ┬╖ Modals `16px` ┬╖ Pills `9999px`
**Shadows:** Cards `0 2px 8px rgba(12,68,124,0.10)` ┬╖ Modals `0 8px 32px rgba(12,68,124,0.16)`
**Spacing base:** 8px
**Theme:** Light only (dark mode toggle exists but design light-first)

